Overview





Essent Group Ltd. (NYSE: ESNT) is a Bermuda-domiciled holding company. Through its subsidiaries, Essent Group serves the housing finance industry by offering mortgage insurance, reinsurance and risk management products to mortgage lenders and investors to support homeownership.
Essent provides private capital to bear mortgage credit risk, enabling lenders and mortgage investors to make mortgage financing available for homeowners.
Essent’s strength is derived from its strong capital position, consistent best-in-class customer service, and collaborative approach to building long-term business relationships.
Essent Group’s major subsidiaries include Essent Guaranty, Inc. and Essent Reinsurance Ltd.







